title: Sojourn (001 - 036 + Prequel) (2001 - 2004)
description:
Sojourn (001 - 036 + Prequel) (2001 - 2004)


The undead warlord Mordath rules the Five Lands with a fist of iron... and sorcery most foul. Fierce and beautiful, Arwyn the archer lost her family to Mordath's unstoppable troll armies. Now Arwyn journeys in search of a mythic hero's arrow of power, the one weapon that can forever end Mordath's reign of fire!
